reviewText: Good movie, not a slick Hollywood production, but good. And I'm not just saying that because I'm in it! I paid to buy it and see it for the first time like anyone else... And I enjoyed it a lot. I always liked Troma Video  releases and this has that same feel (although it is not a Troma Video release).
Cool, campy horror movie.  I sure would hate to run into Voss in a dark alley....yikes!  I'd like to see more from this actor and the director.
